<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Quantaroo - Account Deletion</title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background: #f4f6f8;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.7;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 850px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #374151;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        ol, ul {
            margin-left: 25px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .email {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .email a {
            color: #2563eb;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .email a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .notice {
            background: #eef6ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 25px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">

        <h1>Quantaroo Account Deletion</h1>

        <p>
            Quantaroo is committed to protecting user privacy and providing users with control over their personal data.
        </p>

        <div class="notice">
            Users can permanently delete their account and associated data directly from within the Quantaroo application.
        </div>

        <h2>How to Delete Your Account</h2>

        <ol>
            <li>Open the Quantaroo app.</li>
            <li>Sign in to your account.</li>
            <li>Navigate to <strong>Settings</strong>.</li>
            <li>Select <strong>Delete Account</strong>.</li>
            <li>Confirm the deletion request.</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Data Deleted</h2>

        <p>
            When you delete your account, the following information may be removed:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Account information</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>User preferences and settings</li>
            <li>Associated user-generated data stored by Quantaroo</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Data Retention</h2>

        <p>
            Account deletion requests are processed immediately or within 30 days. Certain information may be retained if required for legal, regulatory, fraud prevention, security, or compliance purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>Need Assistance?</h2>

        <p>
            If you encounter any issues while deleting your account, please contact us:
        </p>

        <p class="email">
            <a href="mailto:helptechxappsbusiness@gmail.com">
                helptechxappsbusiness@gmail.com
            </a>
        </p>

        <div class="footer">
            © 2026 Quantaroo. All Rights Reserved.
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
